{"tid":699104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[日本No老綜？]日本新幹線兇徒失業露宿數月　買新刀登車伺機殺人","createTime":"2018-06-12T08:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T09:05:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5cfa2fb608033a7773bc9d796bf386beb9397554","tid":699104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:47:13.000Z","msg":"JR東海道新幹線列車上周六（9日）發生的隨機殺人案，再有更多內情披露。原來兇徒小島一朗患有精神病，<span style=\"color: red;\">飽受失業之苦並露宿公園長達半年</span>。事發當日他特意買刀，即日前往東京，實行殺人計劃。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，小島自高中畢業後，曾在埼玉縣<span style=\"color: red;\">一間機械修理工場工作，但因遭受欺凌</span>，幹了約一年就辭職，過着居無定所的生活並患上精神病。約兩年前他搬到祖母在愛知縣的家中寄居，去年12月突然出走，到長野一個公園露宿，期間<span style=\"color: red;\">只以由祖母家中帶出來的提款卡作生活費。</span><br />\n<br />\n小島向警方供稱，他在事發當日才前往東京，而兇刀則是出發前始在長野縣購入。在車廂中，小島首先是向兩名女乘客施襲，38歲男死者梅田耕太郎目擊事件想出手制止，結果不敵，反身中十多刀而死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/photo/bknint-20180612003003701-0612_17011_001_01b.jpg?20180612003401\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180612%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180612003003701-0612_17011_001_01b.jpg%3F20180612003401&h=1cbe9650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/bknint-20180612003003701-0612_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180612%2Fbknint-20180612003003701-0612_17011_001.html&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=78447652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/bknint-20180612003003701-0612_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"19032603acbf69a8bfce7eaf24295900c2b20000","tid":699104,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"Future 老貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32702972b10a82e2d7b92340b6582e7c08e10458","tid":699104,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"38歲男死者梅田耕太郎目擊事件想出手制止，結果不敵，反身中十多刀而死。<br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c489399651e20acbbab59518a7dba6cf4c14f9fc","tid":699104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19032603acbf69a8bfce7eaf24295900c2b20000","tid":699104,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"Future 老貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif&h=e4784eb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90b5fe41b7b51eb2dae6c7d92c250309f1291857","tid":699104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19032603acbf69a8bfce7eaf24295900c2b20000","tid":699104,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"Future 老貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"HK is not Japan"},{"pid":"15c9f62dbfd594f182def6ba7df09fea5f4490ba","tid":699104,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"機械修理 = rubbish"},{"pid":"5cabc2d9f0b49a8862e3b874b212807411059ff9","tid":699104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c9f62dbfd594f182def6ba7df09fea5f4490ba","tid":699104,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"機械修理 = rubbish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"IT rubbish too"}]}